information: ETS HUON: Manufacturer of organic fertilizers, soil conditioners - organic and conventional ranges. Huon organic fertilizers are made with the greatest respect to nature. The bases of most of our composts comply with exacting organic farming specifications. Our composting method (with an increase in temperature to 70°C) and cold pelleting, ensure the hygienization of our composts while preserving microbian life.
